snippet.title: Preview of Sneaky Stealy by Ironchest Games
snippet.description:
Sneaky Steal is a game made with PICO-8, by Ironchest Games. This video is intended to preview the game, and foremost to be embedded on sites like itch.io.

https://ironchestgames.itch.io/sneaky-stealy
